## Customization

### Grid Size
Edit these constants in `pathfinding_sfml.cpp`:
```cpp
const int ROWS = 15;        // Number of rows
const int COLS = 30;        // Number of columns
const int CELL_SIZE = 30;   // Pixel size of each cell
```

### Font
The code looks for Arial font at `C:\Windows\Fonts\arial.ttf`. If you have a different font:
```cpp
font.loadFromFile("path/to/your/font.ttf");
```

### Colors
Modify the color values in the `render()` function:
```cpp
if (grid[i][j] == 'S')
    color = sf::Color::Green;  // Change these RGB values
```

## Troubleshooting

### Build Fails
1. Check SFML path in CMakeLists.txt matches your installation
2. Ensure CMake can find gcc: `gcc --version`
3. Delete build folder and try again

### Missing DLLs
1. Copy SFML DLL files from `SFML-3.1.0-windows-gcc-14.2/bin/` to your executable directory:
   - sfml-graphics-3.dll
   - sfml-window-3.dll
   - sfml-system-3.dll

### Font Not Loading
- This is non-critical; the program will still work without fonts
- Change the font path or ensure arial.ttf exists at `C:\Windows\Fonts\arial.ttf`

### Window Won't Respond
- The algorithm runs in the main thread; for long computations, it may appear frozen briefly
- This is normal; it will be responsive again when the algorithm completes

## Algorithm Complexity

| Algorithm | Time Complexity | Space Complexity | Notes |
|-----------|-----------------|------------------|-------|
| A* | O(b^d) | O(n) | Usually fastest with heuristic |
| Dijkstra | O(n²) | O(n) | Always finds optimal path |
| BFS | O(n) | O(n) | Explores uniformly in all directions |

